data.description: Beautiful Updated North Valley Gem!  Open floorplan with 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths and 1 Car Garage.  New tile and carpet throughout.  Fresh paint, new fixtures.  Kitchen is open to living room and has brand new cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  Master with walk in closet and full bath - separate from additional bedrooms.  Bedroom 2 has large sitting room with built ins and extra closet.  Both bathrooms have new vanity sinks and custom tile bath surrounds.  Large laundry area with more cabinet and counter space.
